-- Ebro Foods Says It Has Entered Exclusive Talks to Acquire SunRice Shares
-- B y   W e n d y   P u g h
-- 2010-10-21T02:53:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/ebro-foods-says-it-has-entered-exclusive-talks-to-acquire-sunrice-shares.html
Ricegrowers Ltd., which trades as
SunRice, has entered into exclusive talks with Ebro Foods S.A.,
in relation to an offer to acquire all the shares in SunRice,
according to a statement issued by the Australian company to the
Newcastle Stock Exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wendy Pugh in Melbourne at 
